## 2. Methodology

### 2.1 Data Description

| Column | Description | Data Type |
|--------|-------------|-----------|
| transaction_id | Unique identifier per transaction | String |
| year | Transaction year (2025) | Integer |
| transaction_time | Time of transaction | Time |
| transaction_qty | Quantity purchased | Integer |
| unit_price | Price per unit | Float |
| store_id | Store identifier | String |
| store_location | Physical store location | String |
| product_id | Unique product identifier | String |
| product_category | Broad product group | Categorical |
| product_type | Product variant within category | String |
| product_detail | Detailed attributes (flavor/blend) | String |

**Dataset Statistics:**
- Total Records: 12,847 transactions
- Unique Products: 35 products
- Product Categories: Coffee (18 products), Tea (10 products), Chocolate (7 products)
- Store Locations: Downtown, Uptown, Westside, Eastside, Mall

### 2.2 Key Performance Indicators (KPIs)

| KPI | Formula | Target |
|-----|---------|--------|
| Product Revenue Contribution (%) | (Product Revenue ÷ Total Revenue) × 100 | >2% for hero products |
| Product Sales Volume | Total units sold | - |
| Category Revenue Share | (Category Revenue ÷ Total Revenue) × 100 | <60% dependency |
| Revenue Concentration Ratio | % of products generating 80% revenue | <25% |
| Product Efficiency Score | Revenue ÷ Units Sold | >$4.50 |

### 2.3 Analytical Techniques

#### 2.3.1 Revenue Computation
   Revenue = transaction_qty × unit_price
Total Revenue = $153,431 

#### 2.3.2 Pareto Analysis (80/20 Rule)
Identifies the minimum number of products that contribute to 80% of total revenue. Analysis shows 8 products (23% of total) generate 80.2% of revenue.

#### 2.3.3 Product Efficiency Score
Efficiency Score = Revenue ÷ Units Sold
Average Efficiency Score: $4.82 per unit  
#### 2.3.4 Quadrant Analysis
Products are categorized into four types based on volume and price:
- **Stars:** High volume (>500 units), High price (>$5.00) - 8 products
- **Workhorses:** High volume (>500 units), Low price (≤$5.00) - 12 products
- **Niche:** Low volume (≤500 units), High price (>$5.00) - 6 products
- **Underperformers:** Low volume (≤500 units), Low price (≤$5.00) - 9 products

